<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" lang="it">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>Avviso di Blocco Profilo</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f8f9fa; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">

    <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px 0;">
        <tr>
            <td align="center">

                <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="600" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #e9ecef; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
                    
                    <tr>
                        <td align="center" style="background-color: #ff9411; padding: 30px 20px;">
                            <h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 28px; letter-spacing: 1px;">Volunturing</h1>
                            <p style="color: #ffffff; margin: 5px 0 0 0; font-size: 16px; opacity: 0.9;">La Torino dei Volontari</p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 40px 30px;">
                            <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="color: #212529; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; padding-bottom: 20px;">
                                        Gentilissimo/a,
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td style="color: #495057; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; padding-bottom: 20px;">
                                        La informiamo che il Suo account Volunturing &egrave; stato bloccato con la seguente motivazione:
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                

                                <tr>
                                    <td style="background-color: #fff9f2; border-left: 4px solid #ff9411; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0;">
                                        <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; color: #ff9411; text-transform: uppercase;">Ragione della cancellazione:</p>
                                        <p style="margin: 0; color: #495057; font-style: italic; font-size: 15px;">
                                            "{$reason}"
                                        </p>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>

                                <tr>
                                    <td style="color: #495057; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; padding-top: 30px;">
                                        Se ritiene che si tratti di un errore o di un equivoco, non esiti a contattarci.
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </td>
                    </tr>

                    <tr>
                        <td style="background-color: #212529; padding: 30px; color: #adb5bd; font-size: 12px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5;">
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">
                                <strong>Volontorino OdV</strong><br/>
                                Via dei Volontari, 123 - Torino (TO)
                            </p>
                            <p style="margin: 0;">
                                Ricevi questa email perch&eacute; sei un utente registrato su Volunturing.<br/>
                                &copy; 2025 Volontorino - Tutti i diritti riservati.
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>